individuals - sometimes opposed by the companies themselves.</p>\n<p>In 2020, several companies were found to have severed ties with Trump. For example Les Wexner, ex-CEO of L Brands, which owns Victoria's Secret, and was previously a big donor, left the Republican party after Trumps comments regarding the far-right protest in Charlottesville.</p>\n<p>Grab Your Wallet has an up-to-date <a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1q9QEq3WZQRMaII7TmEk_Fml-u-S2Y0NdL1lsoGmPxi4/edit#gid=0" target="_blank" title="Grab Your Wallet Boycott">list</a> of all companies and organisations to boycott.</p>\n	80	\N	8000000000	1	10	f	t	ethicalconsumer.json#37	\N
